sequenceDiagram
    participant Alice as Alice (Client)
    participant Server as Server (HTTPS)
    participant Bob as Bob (Client)
    
    Note over Alice,Bob: SEND ENCRYPTED MESSAGE
    
    Alice->>Server: GET /public_key/bob
    Server-->>Alice: {bob_public_key}
    
    Alice->>Alice: Generate random AES-256 key
    Alice->>Alice: Encrypt message with AES-GCM<br/>(plaintext → ciphertext + nonce)
    Alice->>Alice: Encrypt AES key with Bob's RSA public key<br/>(aes_key → encrypted_key)
    
    Alice->>Server: POST /send {session_token}<br/>{to: bob, encrypted_key, ciphertext, nonce}
    Server->>Server: Validate session token
    Server->>Server: Check authorization
    Server->>Server: Store encrypted message<br/>(Server CANNOT decrypt!)
    Server-->>Alice: 200 OK - Message stored